	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causam, propter quam ad vos veniunt <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinus</persName> et <persName ref="p1049" cert="high">Farellus</persName>, intelliges ex ipsis, tum quoque quid hic egerint et impetraverint.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mihi propter magna negotia scribere multa nunc non licet.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdeburgensis</placeName> contributio dilata est in conventum 4 Civitatum; sed quando ille fiet?</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nundinę <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Franckfordianę</placeName> appropinquant; opere precium esset prius constitui aliquid.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallo</placeName> ferunt hic, quod magnum in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName> exercitum per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691" cert="high">Lothoringiam</placeName> sit ducturus; <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Danos</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxones</placeName> quoque ascensuros in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916" cert="high">Schertli</persName> hatt von m[einen] herren begert, das man imm <placeName ref="l2" cert="high">Arow</placeName>, <placeName ref="l69" cert="high">Brugg</placeName> oder <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l285" cert="high">Lentzburg</placeName> zuͦ eim musterplatz erlaube; ist imm abgschlagen einstheils von unsers landtvolks anderstheils <foreign xml:lang="la">propter vicinos, quibus hoc nunquam est datum.</foreign></s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto schedulam de inundatione facta in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20" cert="high">Inferiore Germania</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l311" cert="high">Marburgo</placeName> scribunt <persName ref="p18135" cert="high">Lonicerus</persName> et alii 12. ianuarii ita excrevisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l3381" cert="high">Lanum</placeName>, ut lapideum pontem una cum duobus aliis, prae aquarum violentia deiecerit et totam fere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l213" cert="high">Hassiam</placeName> inundarit; tum quoque horrenda audita esse tonitrua et fulgura visa!</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam non sint magni alicuius mali praesagia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic diebus hisce tota civitas nostra fuit in armis et egressa in vicinum campum ad expugnandam arcem quandam ligneam ad hoc factam.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuo, ne hoc quoque aliquid mali portendat.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Abs te avide expecto literas; multo enim iam tempore nihil abs te accepi.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1227" cert="high">Froschoverus</persName> scribit de exemplaribus meis, quę mittat; sed is, cui tradidit, ea <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> reliquit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvi sint fratres omnes, tum quoque tui domestici.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant vos nostri.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 8. martii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] Hallerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt, dafür auf d. Rückseite ein kurzer Brief von <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName>, s. a. folg. Blatt.]</note>
				</p>
